    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_65_3504-3578",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "3504-3578",
      "markText": "她还担心自己恐怕做不到一直不爱女儿。她的想法是，如果我允许自己爱露丝，要是她也出了什么事，我该怎么办？她知道自己根本承受不了再失去一个孩子的打击了。",
      "totalCount": 2160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=3504&rangeEnd=3578",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=3504&rangeEnd=3578"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_61_632-716",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "632-716",
      "markText": "配偶之间决定分居，却还没有走到离婚那一步的时候，总喜欢做出这种可笑的安排。因为在这个阶段，他们仍然觉得孩子和财产是双方共有的，应该慷慨大方地互相分享，没有必要斤斤计较。",
      "totalCount": 1734,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=716",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=716"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_61_3278-3352",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "3278-3352",
      "markText": "露丝·科尔是备受尊敬的严肃小说和国际畅销书作家，但与她的另一成功相比，如此罕见的双重成就也相形见绌，那项了不起的成功就是——她竟然挣扎着长成了大人。",
      "totalCount": 1716,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=3278&rangeEnd=3352",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=3278&rangeEnd=3352"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_59_336-399",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "336-399",
      "markText": "“……至于这位小姐，我能给她的最好祝福， 就是祝她运气差一点儿。”",
      "totalCount": 1694,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=336&rangeEnd=399",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=336&rangeEnd=399"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_102_1200-1285",
      "chapterUid": 102,
      "range": "1200-1285",
      "markText": "“还有什么比两个灵魂的交融更好的事情呢？感受他们的人生融为一体——以彼此的努力互相支持，在悲伤中互相安慰，在痛苦中互相协助，直至最后离别的时刻，在无言的回忆中融为一体。”",
      "totalCount": 1615,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=102&rangeStart=1200&rangeEnd=1285",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=102&rangeStart=1200&rangeEnd=1285"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_112_11129-11172",
      "chapterUid": 112,
      "range": "11129-11172",
      "markText": "不开玩笑——确实到了应该放下的时候。但他永远都放不下玛丽恩，埃迪知道他永远都放不下她。",
      "totalCount": 1598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=112&rangeStart=11129&rangeEnd=11172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=112&rangeStart=11129&rangeEnd=11172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_77_9515-9606",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "9515-9606",
      "markText": "将来有一天，当露丝忘记了大部分照片的模样，她会虚构一切。忘记几乎所有照片之后很久，埃迪也会开始虚构它们的故事。唯独玛丽恩不需要想象托马斯和蒂莫西。当然，露丝也会很快学会想象她的母亲。",
      "totalCount": 1536,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=9515&rangeEnd=9606",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=9515&rangeEnd=9606"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_76_1187-1212",
      "chapterUid": 76,
      "range": "1187-1212",
      "markText": "勇敢就是接受发生在你身上的事——把它尽力做到最好。",
