    {
      "bookmarkId": "909834_62_2608-2653",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "2608-2653",
      "markText": "“嗯。”特德有个话不说完就闭嘴、事情想一半就放下的习惯，他的含混可能半是故意，半是不经心。",
      "totalCount": 1440,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=909834&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=2608&rangeEnd=2653",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/629324505de20a629ae30bd?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=2608&rangeEnd=2653"
